Analysis of ODU Fee
Structure
Group Members: Mounika Kompalli
Sindhuja Gadde
Sruta Keerti Kasula
Motivation behind your topic choice:
1) As International students we pay a lot towards the tuition fees and other mandatory fees.
2) We observe the changes in fee structure every year and often see an increasing trend in
student fees.
3) Example : Fee per credit hour for out-state grad students this year is $1160, and last year was
$1089
4) We were curious to know the breakdown of the student fee structure and also study the need
for increase in the trend of fee over the years.
Description of the data set
Main attributes used in the
visualization of the data are :
1) In-state tuition fee
2) Mandatory fees
3) Student Activity fees.
4) Athletics
5) Health fees.
6) Facilities/Buildings etc
7) Transport fees
Abstract Tasks
1) Where is ODU standing among all other universities in Virginia with respect to fees?
2) Breakdown of student fees that each student pays every semester.
3) Fee trend in last 10 years.
